title: MBMBaM 610: I Don’t Know, My Glasses Were Off
description:
We know that our soothing voices are something that people sometimes fall asleep to, and we can’t help just how calming we are, but the point of this podcast is jokes, okay? So we hope sleep-laughs is a thing.

Suggested talking points: Glue Yourself to Starbucks Challenge, The Looooove Department, MackleLess, That Hair is Ripe, Uneaten Spider Donuts

NARAL Pro-Choice America: https://www.prochoiceamerica.org/
author: shows@mbmbam.com (Griffin McElroy, Justin McElroy, Travis McElroy)
